01:20:43,340 --> 01:20:44,280
In the matter of Keith Lussier

1760
01:20:44,280 --> 01:20:46,693
versus the Good Home Adoption Agency.

1761
01:20:47,900 --> 01:20:50,253
But first of all, I'd
