adoption should be approved.

1771
01:21:12,850 --> 01:21:16,290
And that is, is it or was it benefiting

1772
01:21:16,290 --> 01:21:18,440
the needs and welfare
of the subject child?

1773
01:21:19,420 --> 01:21:22,483
